TY  - JOUR
T1  - New Benchmark Results for the Resource-Constrained Project Scheduling Problem
AU  - Demeulemeester, Erik L.
AU  - Herroelen, Willy S.
Y1  - 1997/11/01
PY  - 1997
DA  - 1997/11/01
